1
00:00:01,170 --> 00:00:01,880
Yeah.

2
00:00:01,880 --> 00:00:03,210
Hey, take me with you!

3
00:00:03,210 --> 00:00:04,250
Oh, sure.

4
00:00:04,250 --> 00:00:05,300
They have them this big?

5
00:00:05,300 --> 00:00:07,010
Oh, but they should have this one, right?

6
00:00:08,340 --> 00:00:09,840
(Calm down.)

7
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:12,180
(We've been hanging out so much lately,
I've lost all perspective.)

8
00:00:12,180 --> 00:00:14,680
(Then again, Yuki
has always been super popular.)

9
00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:16,560
(It'd be weird if he didn't have a girlfriend.)

10
00:00:16,560 --> 00:00:17,760
(Wait, why am I hiding?)

11
00:00:18,290 --> 00:00:20,650
(I should just act natural and say hi.
Something like, "Hey.")

12
00:00:20,650 --> 00:00:24,440
(That's right.
I'll just say hi! Okay!)

13
00:00:28,740 --> 00:00:30,570
- What are you doing?
- Whoa! You scared me!

14
00:00:30,570 --> 00:00:31,950
Seriously, what were you doing?

15
00:00:31,950 --> 00:00:34,870
- I thought you had a stomachache.
- Stop rubbing it! I'm fine!

16
00:00:35,870 --> 00:00:37,160
By the way, where'd that girl go?

17
00:00:37,830 --> 00:00:39,870
Natsu? She went home.

18
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,460
I'll introduce you next time.

19
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:46,340
Oh... okay.

20
00:00:50,590 --> 00:00:53,180
Thanks for today,
for hanging out with me for so long.

21
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:54,970
I should be thanking you.

22
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:58,730
It was my first time helping someone pick things out.
I learned a lot.

23
00:01:00,390 --> 00:01:02,600
Here, this is for you.
